{"tid":1001530,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"樂壇比利 — 譚詠麟","createTime":"2019-01-30T08:23:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T10:18:20.000Z","uid":82917,"like":127,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"873904909241f0239fedff1a4b232efdf81ccff1","tid":1001530,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T08:23:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">祝 福 聲 想 你 都 聽 到</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>1）梁漢文</ins></strong><br />\n譚詠麟早有預感梁漢文受傷 叫娘柄捽碌柚葉洗霉氣！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RSibiX6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRSibiX6.png&h=409f0707&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>2）劉德華</ins></strong><br />\n第一人成功探望華仔的藝人 譚詠麟：華仔講笑會痛！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/30/152926_bca5fa24743930a482a2396f1bae5d5c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F30%2F152926_bca5fa24743930a482a2396f1bae5d5c.png&h=5d406f34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>3）A-Lin</ins></strong><br />\nA-Lin高踭鞋意外卡舞台 譚詠麟尷尬護花幫手拔鞋！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WVFkWNE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWVFkWNE.png&h=43c4bf76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>4）陳貝兒</ins></strong><br />\n譚詠麟拍片賀新人 陳貝兒大讚校長好親民！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H42n99G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH42n99G.png&h=529fd392&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/30/153953_0ed4f59140dd22436556268e925ff20f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F30%2F153953_0ed4f59140dd22436556268e925ff20f.png&h=067abe08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳貝兒揸白色波子不幸被撞！！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>5）李克勤</ins></strong><br />\n李克勤感激譚詠麟帶挈 更被誤會其性取向！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4dh3UD3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4dh3UD3.png&h=1cc4bbd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n送禮指人生中再也找不到另一人跟自己的關係這麼複雜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n左麟右李不再？譚詠麟：覺得好難再搞 克勤慘被拋棄！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j1WgvcR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj1WgvcR.png&h=149051e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n李克勤爆被甘比鬧阻住成條路：廢事嘈！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/30/155018_abc59e1305dbf33ba0a19100458ac114.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F30%2F155018_abc59e1305dbf33ba0a19100458ac114.png&h=8b11113b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XHdyxrt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXHdyxrt.png&h=6615a1ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>6）宣萱</ins></strong><br />\n譚詠麟拉宣萱上台熱舞 令台下歌迷為之瘋狂！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/30/155415_cad7e8241c835de65abba3686147369d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F30%2F155415_cad7e8241c835de65abba3686147369d.png&h=d13d9fdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n宣萱做低頭族落樓梯拗柴 康復期長達半年！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/57LkWUz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F57LkWUz.png&h=655d8235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>7）關楚耀</ins></strong><br />\n契爺譚詠麟力撐新人關楚耀 並百忙之中為他打氣助陣！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6RRXeHs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6RRXeHs.png&h=70873154&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n關楚耀孖女友同遊日本 驚爆藏毒被捕！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HzO6SuG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHzO6SuG.png&h=930f9658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>8）Gin Lee</ins></strong><br />\nGin Lee宣布加盟環球唱片 譚詠麟現身祝賀！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HrQJag9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHrQJag9.png&h=8ff700b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n譚詠麟Gin Lee 新歌疑似抄襲！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/30/160435_8b88a312be91fc29263ea8d1f7469d7b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F30%2F160435_8b88a312be91fc29263ea8d1f7469d7b.png&h=d981c49e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>9）陳奕迅</ins></strong><br />\n老友鬼鬼！「訕王」譚詠麟遇「吹神」陳奕迅一傾就三個鐘！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/30/160845_dc304ac8d0854b14f7b7add2bfc7e119.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F30%2F160845_dc304ac8d0854b14f7b7add2bfc7e119.png&h=6785f03f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/30/160848_9390eafa5cb45a1100fe0dfd3b7a2af1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F30%2F160848_9390eafa5cb45a1100fe0dfd3b7a2af1.png&h=743e3680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n陳奕迅新歌疑似抄襲韓歌 經理人出面否認！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ihDyxxE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FihDyxxE.png&h=27ca4d4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>10）王君馨</ins></strong><br />\n譚詠麟讚王君馨好戲！驚喜回應：多謝譚校長支持<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n痛失女配！王君馨終奪「最受歡迎女角色」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CAiq79t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCAiq79t.png&h=df108dca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>香港醫護界</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/30/153118_d4a0833d60740f14c81fc2e3df18893c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F30%2F153118_d4a0833d60740f14c81fc2e3df18893c.png&h=7bc24ae1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拍片為醫護打氣 譚詠麟開騷後竟不幸中流感！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iXe58av.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiXe58av.png&h=eaee1bc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">各 位 自 求 多 福<br />\n恭 喜 恭 喜 ！！！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b50493bc68f02a98b4132de2245f8884cd7e9d5a","tid":1001530,"uid":117412,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T08:26:03.000Z","msg":"你搵咗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc25f3b14b6d12ed9b6463b349174a42f7c4b65","tid":1001530,"uid":82917,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b50493bc68f02a98b4132de2245f8884cd7e9d5a","tid":1001530,"uid":117412,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T08:26:03.000Z","msg":"你搵咗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T08:31:04.000Z","msg":"睇完幾篇野好想俾牙倫燈一燈我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e3ba8b392dcad931eb3bd61799b76d760ce93a0","tid":1001530,"uid":27064,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime